{"type":"message","id":"84e24e45","parentId":"8185deeb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:36:36.334Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_duk5jflu2lds_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 2960\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/cfi_hybrid_scoring.py' new_len=728\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/cfi_hybrid_scoring.py\r\n[master 6686972] pulse: 2026-03-24 153621\n 6 files changed, 178 insertions(+), 135 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 153621.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 153621.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 153522.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 153621 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed the \"constant format problem\" - tokens with high frequency AND high CFI are metaprogramming artifacts, not meaningful research content. The next step is clearly defined: test hybrid scoring formula that should distinguish constant-format (freq�160, CFI=1) from research trajectory (freq<120, CFI>0.5).\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quick-summit","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 2960\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='experiments/cfi_hybrid_scoring.py' new_len=728\r\n[mutation proposed] experiments/cfi_hybrid_scoring.py\r\n[master 6686972] pulse: 2026-03-24 153621\n 6 files changed, 178 insertions(+), 135 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 153621.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 153621.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 153522.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 153621 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed the \"constant format problem\" - tokens with high frequency AND high CFI are metaprogramming artifacts, not meaningful research content. The next step is clearly defined: test hybrid scoring formula that should